{"type":"message","id":"e1679105","parentId":"a2711f83","timestamp":"2026-02-19T19:32:58.891Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-19 21:32 GMT+2] OPERATION: BLACK SWAN SIMULATION (DEEP THINKING & MOE).\n\n1.  **Harper's Task (Profit Analysis):**\n    *   *Read:* `src/knowledge_base/fees_structure.md`.\n    *   *Calculate:* Profit = `(Sell($2.00) * (1 - Fee)) - Buy($1.20)`.\n    *   *Result:* Margin %.\n\n2.  **Lucas's Task (Circuit Breaker Audit):**\n    *   *Analyze:* Latency 850ms. Error 500 (20% rate).\n    *   *Check:* `api_circuit_breaker.py` config (`failure_threshold=5`, `timeout=60s`).\n    *   *Verdict:* Will it trip? (Yes/No). Is it safe?\n\n3.  **Benjamin's Task (Execution Draft):**\n    *   *Create:* `src/scripts/black_swan_snipe.py` using `pathlib` ONLY.\n    *   *Code:* Import `dmarket_api`, use `create_target`, wrap in `try-except` with `CircuitBreakerOpen` catch.\n\n4.  **Boss's Verdict:**\n    *   Synthesize inputs.\n    *   Decision: BUY or WAIT.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Thinking Block (Theatrical).\n    *   Profit Calc.\n    *   Breaker Status.\n    *   Script Creation Confirmation.\n    *   Final Command."}],"timestamp":1771529578890}}
